Description: Enables gene regulatory network analysis on single cell clusters,
    using 'ANANSE', Xu et al.(2021) <doi:10.1093/nar/gkab598>
    export data from 'Seurat' objects for GRN analysis using 'ANANSE' implemented in 'snakemake',
    and incorporates results for visualization and interpretation.
